  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A roguelike survival adventure inspired by Robinson Crusoe — where every decision matters, and every mistake can cost you everything.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/8c133764b128f9e42e56c7540c045d13.avif?t=1774015801\" width=801 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You step into the role of Daniel, a merchant cast ashore in the 17th century and forced into a brutal fight for survival. Unprepared for the wilderness, you must trust your instincts, learn through failure, adapt to ever-changing dangers, and endure a world that shows no mercy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/1d999c1477172a534d73723f71e0993d.poster.avif?t=1774015801\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/1d999c1477172a534d73723f71e0993d.webm?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/1d999c1477172a534d73723f71e0993d.mp4?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/a61f645fbf0ea9bc8cccccfc105323a0.avif?t=1774015801\" width=801 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A highly realistic, systems-driven world where everything reacts. Day and night cycles, weather, fire, and liquids interact in complex ways - creating endless, unpredictable challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The island can be explored freely. Beaches, riverlands, jungle, and other biomes offer different resources. Every interaction encourages experimentation and instinctive problem solving. You just have to be creative.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/7a7cfe6a1e2b2be54a46709fbaf13880.poster.avif?t=1774015801\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/7a7cfe6a1e2b2be54a46709fbaf13880.webm?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/7a7cfe6a1e2b2be54a46709fbaf13880.mp4?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/912e75648a1ed7af6cd28219c1a12886.avif?t=1774015801\" width=801 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every failure is a lesson. Learn, adapt, and return wiser and better equipped each time. The island is relentless — prowling predators, violent storms, sickness, territorial threats, poisonous plants, and tense encounters with a local tribe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No two runs are the same. Resources, weather, and dangers shift with every attempt, forcing you to rethink how you survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/732708c847695da40670110825abf091.poster.avif?t=1774015801\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/732708c847695da40670110825abf091.webm?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/732708c847695da40670110825abf091.mp4?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/e23d0da163f8609e535691a4b9d421a0.avif?t=1774015801\" width=801 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the past of a stranded survivor — the life before the shipwreck and the uncertain future ahead. As you explore, piece together who you are, why you were on the ship, and whether your arrival on the island is mere coincidence or something far more meaningful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are signs of others. Whether they become allies or enemies depends entirely on you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/3d879712c23c8d4daafcb28a1af8507f.poster.avif?t=1774015801\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/3d879712c23c8d4daafcb28a1af8507f.webm?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/3d879712c23c8d4daafcb28a1af8507f.mp4?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/c308ee48f133b2d196e910bb0994c46f.avif?t=1774015801\" width=801 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tailor the experience to your playstyle. Adjust day length, world intensity, and survival systems to shape the journey you want — whether you crave a relentless challenge or prefer a slower, exploration and base-building focused adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/54f90fdba9f72c8e8b6150df80596d7d.poster.avif?t=1774015801\" width=1170 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/54f90fdba9f72c8e8b6150df80596d7d.webm?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/54f90fdba9f72c8e8b6150df80596d7d.mp4?t=1774015801\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/b531339e98d9710b08bd8ca92626075c.avif?t=1774015801\" width=801 height=89 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/16e993c1cf533f0f401ab767feba7d75.avif?t=1774015801\" width=800 height=210 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Co-funded by the European Union. Co-funded by European Union Creative Europe Media.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1942110/extras/1eb2415395ab5b0e144345f9b32b9175.webp?t=1774015801\" width=302 height=60 /></span></p>",
